s-keyword">return</span> result;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(array,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;未处理数组&#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(sliceArr(array, size),<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;新数组-分组后的&#x27;</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
